title: Total population of Amsterdam 2009 to 2019
summary: The chart at hand is a line chart where the x axis denotes Year and a y axis denotes Number of inhabitants. In total the number of data points it has is 11.
In general Number of inhabitants has rose over the Year.
Number of inhabitants is slightly increasing from 2009 to 2019.
The steepest increase occurs in between the Year 2010 and 2011.
Maximum Number of inhabitants, about 862965.0 was reported at Year 2019
The lowest Number of inhabitants, of value 755605.0 was reported at Year 2009
